Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.27,0:01:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We aren't needed in\Nouter space Heero!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.14,0:01:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We mustn't fight each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.12,0:01:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Relena...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.57,0:02:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.04,0:02:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I still don't know where\NHeero has gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.87,0:02:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't laugh, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.84,0:02:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I can still hear\NHeero's voice even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.95,0:02:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.21,0:02:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe he'll come here\Nto the Sanc Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.45,0:02:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how much time\Nhas passed...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.06,0:02:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...since we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.60,0:02:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It was during my shuttle\Nflight with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.37,0:02:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...on our way back to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.38,0:02:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.91,0:02:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That was when I first came\Nacross the shooting star...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.62,0:02:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...Heero Yuy, who carried\Nthe colonies' hopes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.62,0:03:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,One more to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.14,0:03:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where everything\Nstarted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,My code name: Heero Yuy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.51,0:03:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I was given one mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.45,0:03:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,To destroy OZ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He's still just a young boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.76,0:04:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.80,0:04:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,See what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They're down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.70,0:04:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.04,0:04:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.64,0:04:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.85,0:04:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.22,0:04:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Relena Darlian.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.39,0:04:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Until then, I enjoyed\Na world of happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.50,0:04:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignorant of the world and\Ngiving nothing to society.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But meeting him greatly\Nchanged my destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.67,0:04:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.88,0:05:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Heero Yuy.\NIt's a pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.55,0:05:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.96,0:05:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.53,0:05:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my birthday tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.77,0:05:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you'll be able to\Nmake it to the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.45,0:05:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.99,0:05:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't the only Gundam pilot\Nthat landed on Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.19,0:05:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...as part of Operation Meteor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.36,0:05:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There was also Trowa Barton,\Npilot of the Gundam Heavyarms.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.44,0:06:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Quatre Raberba Winner,\Npilot of the Gundam Sandrock.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.87,0:06:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.15,0:06:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.88,0:06:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I shouldn't be fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.70,0:06:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Put your hands down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the first one to surrender\Nand come out, remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stop! Stop or I'll shoot!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's just a young kid!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.36,0:07:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A kid did all that damage to{\i0}\N{\i1}the base by himself? :!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? A woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.80,0:07:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wu Fei Chang, pilot of\Nthe Shenlong Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.34,0:07:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where's this light coming from?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the enemy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.14,0:07:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And Duo Maxwell, pilot of\Nthe Gundam Deathscythe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.85,0:07:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.62,0:07:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.59,0:07:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are torpedoes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.02,0:07:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.89,0:08:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.86,0:08:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk to me, Heero!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.96,0:08:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Relena...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.83,0:08:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.57,0:08:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in too deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty obvious that\Nyou're the bad guy here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.55,0:08:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.32,0:08:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero! Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.39,0:08:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't overdo it; remember,\Nyou're injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.07,0:08:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you wanna\Nshoot him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.84,0:08:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.37,0:08:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.84,0:08:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady, I'm sure you have your\Nreasons for being here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.98,0:08:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...but you'd better just leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.21,0:08:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Do yourself a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:08:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't had enough?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.35,0:09:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't consider the other\NGundam pilots my comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.69,0:09:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I never had any comrades\Nfrom the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.13,0:09:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like Relena, this guy\Nwho calls himself Duo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.43,0:09:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...is merely an obstacle\Nto my mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.73,0:09:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, everything is finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mission complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.68,0:09:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, that was when you\Nstrongly wished for peace...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...between Earth and\Nthe colonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.86,0:09:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We've heard everything\Nyou have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.16,0:09:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to leave the room\Nnow, Vice Foreign Minister.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.26,0:09:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it about time you\Npeople realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.87,0:09:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...that you're posing the\Ngreatest threat of all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.00,0:09:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And Father, you flew with\Nme to space once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.07,0:09:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That turned out to be\Nyour last gift of kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.61,0:10:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,To show me just how\Nbeautiful the Earth was.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.19,0:10:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing\Nwith my father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.89,0:10:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Relena...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.73,0:10:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not your biological\Nfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Your real name is\NRelena Peacecraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.14,0:10:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the daughter of\Nthe Peacecraft family...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...who once advocated\NTotal Pacifism.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.38,0:10:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.35,0:10:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out for the\NOZ organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.09,0:10:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.39,0:10:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,NO!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:11:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Delete files on Heero Yuy\Nat the Saint Gabriel Institute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.24,0:11:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Transfer procedures complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.28,0:11:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you off to fight again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.01,0:11:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's your next mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.45,0:11:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd come across too many\Nof his secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.66,0:11:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But the fact that Heero\Nwas a Gundam pilot...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.46,0:11:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...sent from the colonies...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.59,0:11:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...might have influenced\Nmy personal situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.40,0:11:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...in regards to how I was\Ngoing to live out my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero, I know too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You still gonna kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.08,0:11:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.62,0:11:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Before, I didn't want to die\Nwithout any answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.62,0:11:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But now it's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.29,0:11:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I know how you\Nfeel when you fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.72,0:11:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm now fighting with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.09,0:11:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,With me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.92,0:12:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.92,0:12:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be better off if she died!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.76,0:12:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.89,0:13:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.06,0:13:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.17,0:13:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Please Heero.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.13,0:13:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Marshal Noventa...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...Chief Commander of the\NUnited Earth Sphere Alliance...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...pushed for peace\Nwith the colonies...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.30,0:13:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,...and planned a significant\Nreduction in armaments.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.27,0:13:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Commander in Chief\Nof OZ, Treize Khushrenada...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.81,0:13:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...shrewdly released some\Ninformation...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.78,0:13:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...to lure the Gundams to\Nthe New Edwards Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.45,0:13:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And tricked them into killing\Nthe Alliance Military leaders.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.17,0:14:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be rash now, young man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The second act has just begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.28,0:14:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be getting busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.82,0:14:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Operation Daybreak...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This scrupulously planned\Ncoup d'etat allowed OZ...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.12,0:14:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...with soldiers assigned at\NAlliance Military Bases...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.09,0:14:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...under the guise of\NSpecials soldiers...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...to overthrow the Alliance\Nin just one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.37,0:14:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.23,0:14:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Just see for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.77,0:14:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The era of the Alliance\Nhas ended!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Our OZ organization must\Ngive rise to a true alliance!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.95,0:14:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition, Colonel Une\Nproposed a plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.09,0:15:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,...to transfer Taurus space\Nsuits to the Siberia Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.66,0:15:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But this was also a deceptive\Noperation...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...to annihilate the Gundams.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.87,0:15:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You think the other\NGundams will come?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't win by ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.74,0:15:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm positive the others\Nwill come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.20,0:15:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.53,0:15:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll fight for recognition\Nof superiority.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that'll suit you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You ARE a Gundam pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,0:16:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would've guessed\NGundams had this much power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Get Space Fortress Barge\Non line!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.12,0:16:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Calling all Gundam pilots.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.79,0:16:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're ready to stage an all-out{\i0}\N{\i1}missile attack on the colonies!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I demand all pilots to\Nsurrender at once...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.17,0:16:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...and hand over your Gundams!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.34,0:16:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They've targeted the colonies!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand over our Gundams?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.61,0:16:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like OZ's tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.88,0:16:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys can't fight, can you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.59,0:16:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Attention OZ.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.12,0:16:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never imagined you people{\i0}\N{\i1}could be so foolish.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.13,0:16:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To you, inhumane moves like{\i0}\N{\i1}colony assaults are justified...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...if that's what it takes for{\i0}\N{\i1}you to come out victorious.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.43,0:16:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have no choice but{\i0}\N{\i1}to surrender.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.00,0:16:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I will not hand over{\i0}\N{\i1}the Gundams. I repeat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.07,0:16:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I surrender, but I will not{\i0}\N{\i1}hand over the Gundams.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.28,0:17:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mission accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.25,0:17:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Off to fight again, Heero?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.18,0:17:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm headed for\Nmy own battleground.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.52,0:17:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The Romefeller Foundation\Nsought to maintain peace...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,...by dominating others.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That may be possible as long\Nas they keep winning battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.40,0:17:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But as Relena Peacecraft,\Nleader of Sanc Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:18:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...I can't allow them to reign\Nat the cost of many lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.77,0:18:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I was defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.07,0:18:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the colonies were\Nbeing used as a shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.38,0:18:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But Zechs repaired\Nmy Gundam...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.45,0:18:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...hoping to end our\Nunfinished battle in Siberia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.08,0:18:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The battle took place\Nin Antarctica.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.75,0:18:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I refused to accept charity\Nfrom Zechs...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.69,0:18:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...and challenged him in\NTrowa's Gundam Heavyarms.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But this battle was meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.86,0:18:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Between a man looking\Nfor something to protect...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.43,0:18:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...and a man who had lost\Nall means to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.09,0:18:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A mistaken past is difficult\Nfor anyone to swallow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.42,0:18:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're still young.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.73,0:18:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We should be thinking\Nof building the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.86,0:18:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.46,0:19:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to end this\Nmeaningless fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.53,0:19:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Has it begun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's more like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.56,0:20:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This'll finish you off!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.63,0:20:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.03,0:20:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop this battle immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.34,0:20:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,See for yourself how dirty\Nand foul battles really are!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.24,0:20:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're a true warrior\Nand a Peacecraft knight...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.35,0:20:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...you couldn't possibly\Nuse such foul play!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.82,0:20:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Relena, call from\NLieutenant Noin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.66,0:20:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Noin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.49,0:20:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I misunderstood you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.76,0:20:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were sincere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.33,0:20:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Precisely.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.23,0:20:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I deserve your contempt,{\i0}\N{\i1}but I can't help myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.37,0:20:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I believe in Colonel Zechs!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.37,0:20:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not about to interrupt{\i0}\N{\i1}any of his plans.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.31,0:20:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.27,0:20:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Defeat Zechs!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.87,0:20:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Relena!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.01,0:20:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But Relena, no matter what tricks\Nof fate you have been through...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.65,0:21:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...please don't wish for\Nyour brother's death!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.55,0:21:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother...he's my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.12,0:21:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned then for\Nthe first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.46,0:21:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...that Zechs was my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Numerous carriers approaching\Nfrom 3 o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.20,0:21:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.17,0:21:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you read me, Heero{\i0}\N{\i1}and Zechs?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thirty suits in flight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.17,0:21:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A hundred if they unload{\i0}\N{\i1}all Aries suits.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.14,0:21:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll attract them away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.94,0:21:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Glory to the colonies!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.71,0:21:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Heero!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.41,0:21:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll meet again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.91,0:21:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Zechs!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.92,0:21:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time I fight him...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.32,0:21:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...will he be Zechs Merquise\Nor Milliardo Peacecraft?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.92,0:21:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, I'll defeat him\Nif he's in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.13,0:21:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's an enemy, I'll kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.30,0:21:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen Heero\Nor my brother since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.93,0:21:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, with OZ splitting\Ninto two factions...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.30,0:21:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...and continuing their\Nfoolish battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.27,0:21:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...the world is headed\Neven further toward chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.54,0:21:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.44,0:22:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll come back to me, Heero.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.41,0:22:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,To end this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.22,0:22:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.42,0:22:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm waiting for you to\Nhurry and return to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.82,0:23:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as mankind\Nexists in this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.89,0:23:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...there will always be battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.36,0:23:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And denouncing battles\Nwill never lead to peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.03,0:23:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Treize Khushrenada has\Ndisappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.20,0:23:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...from the center stage\Nof history.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.57,0:23:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But while destinies slip\Npast one another...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.30,0:23:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...Treize begins to proceed\Nwith new plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.64,0:23:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, on Gundam Wing, Episode 28,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.08,0:23:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"Passing Destinies".
